Package: slowraker
Type: Package
Title: A Slow Implementation of the Rapid Automatic Keyword Extraction (RAKE) 
    Algorithm 
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person("Christopher", "Baker", email = "chriscrewbaker@gmail.com",
    role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Provides a mostly pure-R implementation of the RAKE algorithm, 
    which can be used to extract keywords from documents without any training 
    data.
URL: https://github.com/crew102/slowraker
BugReports: https://github.com/crew102/slowraker/issues
